  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/98e0837533ddf36caacb01d233bd3355.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/98e0837533ddf36caacb01d233bd3355.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Customize Your Character</strong><br>Define your style before you start! Choose your hair, clothes, and accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/b4eabaa5ddcf27976026eecd3f3863e4.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/b4eabaa5ddcf27976026eecd3f3863e4.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/b4eabaa5ddcf27976026eecd3f3863e4.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Open and Customize Your Shop</strong><br>Get an empty shop and design it your way. Shelves, decor, and signs are all yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/ebb3e3cdd4a008d279a821cb261b0f02.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/ebb3e3cdd4a008d279a821cb261b0f02.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/ebb3e3cdd4a008d279a821cb261b0f02.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Clean Your Shop</strong><br>Pick up trash and keep it tidy. A clean shop means happy customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/aa188efa45e3c77850778dd0fdbb4515.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/aa188efa45e3c77850778dd0fdbb4515.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/aa188efa45e3c77850778dd0fdbb4515.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Bargain and Trade</strong><br>Negotiate with customers. Buy cheap, sell high, and maximize your profit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/96a3f3f923a700e4caa91ac26da90f0b.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/96a3f3f923a700e4caa91ac26da90f0b.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/96a3f3f923a700e4caa91ac26da90f0b.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Auctions</strong><br>Join auctions for rare items. Bid smart and grab the best deals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/6d698b484903d5b823f75ca805df3664.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/6d698b484903d5b823f75ca805df3664.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/6d698b484903d5b823f75ca805df3664.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Storage Wars</strong><br>Compete for items in storage units. Be the first to claim valuable loot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/0dd024177f988f99ba6f62689a3d2e1b.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/0dd024177f988f99ba6f62689a3d2e1b.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/0dd024177f988f99ba6f62689a3d2e1b.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Races and Competition</strong><br>Join street races in the city. Be fast, win big!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/63757d0d1b8a0e5192d9bd9503bceb57.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/63757d0d1b8a0e5192d9bd9503bceb57.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/63757d0d1b8a0e5192d9bd9503bceb57.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Fishing</strong><br>Cast your line at the lake. Catch rare fish and relax while earning!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/e82e14eaee3c486504af99e5e8957fe0.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/e82e14eaee3c486504af99e5e8957fe0.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/e82e14eaee3c486504af99e5e8957fe0.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Pizza Delivery</strong><br>Deliver on time and collect tips. The faster you are, the more you earn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/18491e4d5d4ab0104912144bcb17062e.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/18491e4d5d4ab0104912144bcb17062e.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/18491e4d5d4ab0104912144bcb17062e.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Shipment & Loading Jobs</strong><br>Carry crates and load trucks. Hard work pays too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/acdd5f4168988d145c43954b79159f83.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=601 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/acdd5f4168988d145c43954b79159f83.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Card Games</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try your luck with cards and build the best hand. Big rewards may be one move away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/21822b954e918936f53c7457c4229084.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/21822b954e918936f53c7457c4229084.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/21822b954e918936f53c7457c4229084.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Scratch Cards</strong><br>Scratch to reveal surprises. If lucky, win big!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Coin Flip Bets</strong><br>Simple but thrilling! Heads or tails? Bet and double your money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/f76d87ae2059252bc74105307318fd80.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/f76d87ae2059252bc74105307318fd80.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/f76d87ae2059252bc74105307318fd80.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/98e0837533ddf36caacb01d233bd3355.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/98e0837533ddf36caacb01d233bd3355.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Customize Your Character</strong><br>Define your style before you start! Choose your hair, clothes, and accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/b4eabaa5ddcf27976026eecd3f3863e4.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/b4eabaa5ddcf27976026eecd3f3863e4.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/b4eabaa5ddcf27976026eecd3f3863e4.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Open and Customize Your Shop</strong><br>Get an empty shop and design it your way. Shelves, decor, and signs are all yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/ebb3e3cdd4a008d279a821cb261b0f02.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=1280 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/ebb3e3cdd4a008d279a821cb261b0f02.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/ebb3e3cdd4a008d279a821cb261b0f02.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Clean Your Shop</strong><br>Pick up trash and keep it tidy. A clean shop means happy customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/aa188efa45e3c77850778dd0fdbb4515.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/aa188efa45e3c77850778dd0fdbb4515.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/aa188efa45e3c77850778dd0fdbb4515.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Bargain and Trade</strong><br>Negotiate with customers. Buy cheap, sell high, and maximize your profit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/96a3f3f923a700e4caa91ac26da90f0b.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/96a3f3f923a700e4caa91ac26da90f0b.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/96a3f3f923a700e4caa91ac26da90f0b.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Auctions</strong><br>Join auctions for rare items. Bid smart and grab the best deals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/6d698b484903d5b823f75ca805df3664.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/6d698b484903d5b823f75ca805df3664.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/6d698b484903d5b823f75ca805df3664.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Storage Wars</strong><br>Compete for items in storage units. Be the first to claim valuable loot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/0dd024177f988f99ba6f62689a3d2e1b.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/0dd024177f988f99ba6f62689a3d2e1b.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/0dd024177f988f99ba6f62689a3d2e1b.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Races and Competition</strong><br>Join street races in the city. Be fast, win big!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/63757d0d1b8a0e5192d9bd9503bceb57.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/63757d0d1b8a0e5192d9bd9503bceb57.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/63757d0d1b8a0e5192d9bd9503bceb57.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Fishing</strong><br>Cast your line at the lake. Catch rare fish and relax while earning!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/e82e14eaee3c486504af99e5e8957fe0.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/e82e14eaee3c486504af99e5e8957fe0.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/e82e14eaee3c486504af99e5e8957fe0.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Pizza Delivery</strong><br>Deliver on time and collect tips. The faster you are, the more you earn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/18491e4d5d4ab0104912144bcb17062e.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/18491e4d5d4ab0104912144bcb17062e.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/18491e4d5d4ab0104912144bcb17062e.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Shipment & Loading Jobs</strong><br>Carry crates and load trucks. Hard work pays too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/acdd5f4168988d145c43954b79159f83.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=601 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/acdd5f4168988d145c43954b79159f83.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Card Games</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try your luck with cards and build the best hand. Big rewards may be one move away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/21822b954e918936f53c7457c4229084.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/21822b954e918936f53c7457c4229084.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/21822b954e918936f53c7457c4229084.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Scratch Cards</strong><br>Scratch to reveal surprises. If lucky, win big!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔸 <strong>Coin Flip Bets</strong><br>Simple but thrilling! Heads or tails? Bet and double your money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/f76d87ae2059252bc74105307318fd80.poster.avif?t=1774311331\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/f76d87ae2059252bc74105307318fd80.webm?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608020/extras/f76d87ae2059252bc74105307318fd80.mp4?t=1774311331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
